## Dependencies
node_modules/
.pnp/
.pnp.*
.yarn/

## Build output
dist/
build/
*.tsbuildinfo

## Phase 23e runtime build cache. The studio esbuilds client modules
## from public/src/ into <pluginRoot>/.runtime-cache/dist/ at boot.
## Never committed; populated on first run, reused on warm boots.
plugins/deskwork-studio/.runtime-cache/

## Plugin shell runtime install artifacts. The bin shim runs
## `npm install --omit=dev` at first invocation to materialize
## @deskwork/<pkg>@<version> into the plugin's own node_modules tree,
## which generates a package-lock.json next to the plugin's
## package.json. The shell's package.json is intentionally empty (no
## deps); the lockfile describes the runtime-installed graph and
## should never be committed.
plugins/*/package-lock.json

## scope-discovery install manifest. Per-worktree transactional state
## recording which files `install-scope-discovery-hooks` (and the paired
## `install-agent-prompts`) wrote into THIS worktree. Contains absolute
## paths that are meaningless in any other worktree; committing it
## pollutes new worktrees with stale cross-worktree entries on every
## re-install. The journal preserves any audit need; the manifest itself
## is reachable runtime state, not source-of-truth.
.dw-lifecycle/scope-discovery/hooks-installed.json

## scope-discovery orchestrator-loop durable runtime state. The
## orchestrator-turn CLI verb persists loop-state, controller-state,
## audit watermarks, and audit-request artifacts under these paths.
## Per-worktree state; never committed.
.dw-lifecycle/scope-discovery/orchestrator-runtime/
.dw-lifecycle/scope-discovery/pending-audits/
.dw-lifecycle/scope-discovery/resolved-escalations/

## scope-discovery synthesizer output. `scope-inventory` writes the
## manifest + run-history under the feature's docs dir. Regenerated on
## each invocation; never committed.
docs/*/001-IN-PROGRESS/*/scope-manifest.yaml
docs/*/001-IN-PROGRESS/*/scope-inventory/

## Runtime / local state
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

## Editors / OS
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

## Worktree-local commit-message scratch file (per .claude/rules/file-handling.md).
## Subagents write multi-line commit messages here, then 'git commit -F' from it.
.git-commit-msg.tmp

## Claude Code local
.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/settings.local.json~
.claude/worktrees/

## Codex local
.agents/.tmp/
## Agent memory belongs in ~/.claude/projects/, never committed
/memory/

## Playwright MCP local scratch (screenshots, console logs, page snapshots
## generated during dogfood UX sessions). Never committed.
.playwright-mcp/

## Session-paperwork screenshots dropped at repo root during dogfood walks
## (no intentional root-level PNGs exist; subdirectory PNGs under docs/ +
## plugins/ are not affected by the leading slash anchor).
/*.png

## Superpowers brainstorming companion mockups (visual session content).
.superpowers/

## Local dogfood sandbox — a clone of audiocontrol.org used to drive the
## editorial-calendar lifecycle end-to-end against a real-shaped project
## tree. Lives inside this worktree (not a sibling) to avoid confusion
## with other audiocontrol.org worktrees and to keep tool-permission
## scope inside one directory. Never committed.
/.audiocontrol.org/

# WebKit probe screenshots + JSON dumps written by scripts/probe-*.mjs.
# Per-session output, never committed.
/tmp/

## jscpd duplication report — regenerated on every detect-clones run;
## the canonical baseline lives in .dw-lifecycle/scope-discovery/clones.yaml.
/reports/

## /loop scheduler lockfile — runtime artifact, never committed.
/.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

## Stray pnpm lockfile — this project uses npm workspaces, not pnpm.
/pnpm-lock.yaml
.audit-find-refs.sh
